---
title: One-Pot Mexican Bacon & Black Bean Soup with Veggies, Cheddar Cheese & Corn Chips
description: This flavour combo is a beloved companion to many dishes like enchiladas, nachos and tacos. In the colder weather though, why not try this tomato black bean and veggie delight in a soup? It won’t disappoint, in fact it may be the new way to eat beans, veggies and cheese.

